snippet.title: SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS - Summer Game Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
3 Hedgehogs. 2 Epic Adventures. 1 Ultimate Collection.

SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS is available October 25th, pre-order today to receive the epic Sonic Adventure Legacy Skin!

Visit https://sonicxshadowgenerations.com to learn more!
